\subsubsection parameters ROS parameters

Reads and maintains the following parameters on the ROS server

- \b "~linear_threshold" : \b [double] linear threshold min: -std::numeric_limits<double>::infinity(), default: 0.0, max: std::numeric_limits<double>::infinity()
- \b "~angular_threshold" : \b [double] angular threshold min: -std::numeric_limits<double>::infinity(), default: 0.0, max: std::numeric_limits<double>::infinity()
- \b "~threshold" : \b [double] threshold for double min: -std::numeric_limits<double>::infinity(), default: 0.0, max: std::numeric_limits<double>::infinity()

